程序包 org.elasticsearch.test.rest

Infrastructure for testing REST. See ESRestTestCase for running tests against an Elasticsearch cluster using the REST tests and the rest of the package for mocking utilities.
  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    ESRestTestCase
    Superclass for tests that interact with an external test cluster using Elasticsearch's RestClient.
    ESRestTestCase.VersionSensitiveWarningsHandler
    Helper class to check warnings in REST responses with sensitivity to versions used in the target cluster.
    FakeRestChannel  
    FakeRestRequest  
    FakeRestRequest.Builder  
    RestActionTestCase
    A common base class for Rest*ActionTests.
